    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Designates informal eating facilities with plated table service, a limited food-oriented menu generally of simply prepared items and coffee, and a social atmosphere emphasizing bustle and noise.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
